<h1>Editions</h1>
<p class="subhead">Field guides do not end; they have editions.</p>

<p>
  When the Publisher judges the manuscript ready, a First Edition is cut
  into <code>editions/</code>, possibly printed and bound, and the archive
  immediately continues toward the Second. Reclassifications between
  editions are not errata. They are content.
</p>

<p>
  <em>No edition has been cut yet. The First is in compilation.</em>
</p>
